                Mr. Noel-Baker
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-df3c10bf-6099-4237-b971-44e2f98505de" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
